Package com.gams.api

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GAMSCheckpoint
    An instance of GAMSCheckpoint captures the state of a GAMSJob after the GAMSJob.run() method has been carried out, and can be created via the call of methods.
    GAMSDatabase
    An instance of GAMSDatabase communicates data between the Java world and the GAMS world.
    GAMSDatabaseDomainViolation
    An instance of GAMSDatabaseDomainViolation stores a domain violation information for each symbol in a GAMSDatabase instance.
    GAMSDatabaseIterator
    An iterator of a GAMSDatabase over a collection of GAMSSymbol.
    GAMSEquation
    This is the representation of an equation symbol in GAMS.
    GAMSEquationRecord
    This is the representation of a single record of a GAMSEquation instance.
    GAMSGlobals
    GAMSGlobals defines constants that are used by com.gams.api package.
    GAMSJob
    An instance of GAMSJob manages the execution of a GAMS program given by GAMS model source.
    GAMSModelInstance
    A GAMSJob is the standard way of dealing with a GAMS model and the corresponding solution provided by a solver.
    GAMSModelInstanceOpt
    The GAMSModelInstanceOpt can be used to customize the GAMSModelInstance.solve() routine.
    GAMSModifier
    Instances of this class are input to GAMSModelInstance.instantiate method.
    GAMSOptions
    The GAMSOptions class manages GAMS options (sometimes also called GAMSParameter, since they correspond to the command line parameters of the GAMS executable) for a GAMSJob and GAMSModelInstance.
    GAMSParameter
    This is the representation of a parameter symbol in GAMS.
    GAMSParameterRecord
    This is the representation of a single record of a GAMSParameter instance.
    GAMSSet
    This is the representation of a set symbol in GAMS.
    GAMSSetRecord
    This is the representation of a single record of a GAMSSet instance.
    GAMSSymbol<T extends GAMSSymbolRecord>
    This is the representation of a symbol in GAMS.
    GAMSSymbolDomainViolation
    An instance of GAMSSymbolDomainViolation stores a domain violation information for a GAMSSymbol instance.
    GAMSSymbolIterator<T extends GAMSSymbolRecord>
    An iterator of a GAMSymbol over a collection of GAMSSymbolRecord.
    GAMSSymbolRecord
    This is the representation of a single record of a GAMSSymbol instance.
    GAMSVariable
    This is the representation of a variable symbol in GAMS.
    GAMSVariableRecord
    This is the representation of a single record of a GAMSVariable instance.
    GAMSWorkspace
    The GAMSWorkspace is the base class in the com.gams.api package.
    GAMSWorkspaceInfo
    The GAMSWorkspaceInfo can be used as input parameter for the GAMSWorkspace constructor.
